snippet.title: Zenless Zone Zero Tuning Test Trailer - Don't Mess Up Your First Commission
snippet.description:
Distinguished Proxies,
Zenless Zone Zero's Tuning Test has already begun!
We're honored to welcome you all to New Eridu! Your fearlessness has shown your determination. We don't want to dwell on the dangers of the Hollows, but whatever your reason for entering the unknown, we wish you luck!
Enough chit-chat now, enjoy the game!

—Welcome to New Eridu!—

Follow the official Zenless Zone Zero community for more prizes and events:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ZZZ_EN
Discord: https://discord.gg/zenlesszonezero
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/ZZZ_Official/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ZZZ.Official.EN
Tik Tok: https://www.tiktok.com/@zzz

#ZZZ #ZZZERO
